snippet.title: Sonic Dream Team - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Join Sonic and friends as they dive deep into the bizarre world of Eggman’s dreams!  

Sonic Dream Team is now available on Apple Arcade!

Grab Sonic Dream Team today: https://apple.co/sonic-dream-team

Check out our other social pages to stay up-to-date on the latest Sonic happenings:
